===Etymology===
First attested in 1657.
* Perhaps from {{etyl|la|en}} {{m|la|abnegō||to refuse, reject}} from {{m|la|ab||away from}} + {{m|la|negō||to deny}},<ref>{{R:OCD2|page=3}}.</ref><ref name=SOED>{{R:SOED5|page=6}}</ref>
* Alternatively, perhaps a {{back-form|abnegation|lang=en|nocap=1}}<ref>{{R:CDOE|page=3}}</ref><ref>{{R:MW3 1976|page=4}}</ref>

